<title>SWITZERLAND: RESEARCH ALERT-UBS repeats hold for Roche.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-UBS repeats hold for Roche.</headline>
<dateline>ZURICH 1997-07-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>UBS left its earnings estimates unchanged and repeated its hold recommendation for Roche Holding AG after the company reported first-half sales rose around 20 percent.</p>
<p>&quot;First-half sales growth of 19.5 percent to 9.3 billion (versus our estimate of 18 percent to 9.2 billion) was slightly better than expected. Given the only slight differences we are leaving our forecasts unchanged and still recommend holding Roche,&quot; analysts Birgit Kulhoff and Charlotte Moore wrote.</p>
<p>UBS gave these estimates:</p>
<p>		Net profit (million Sfr)    EPS	P/E    Div</p>
<p> 1997	     4,520		   524	27.5    93</p>
<p> 1998	     5,047		   585	24.7   105</p>
<p> 1999	     5,829		   676	21.3   120</p>
<p>-- Zurich newsroom +41 1 631 7340</p>
